data.description: Under contract-accepting backup offers. *****TAKE a LOOK at Virtual Tour Link 1***  WELCOME HOME  to this Gorgeous 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home in sought after neighborhood of Arlington Ridge.... this home has it all... including many updates, MOTORIZED blind and shades, luxury wood look vinyl flooring throughout the  Family/Dining AREA and master bedroom,  great size garage for your car and golf cart was built in 2016.The kitchen features elegant cabinetry with soft-close drawers, doors, and QUARTZ countertops. New Stainless-Steel appliances (Refrigerator, Dishwasher & front load pedestal Washer& Dryer) has a gas range, and large pantry. A generous eat in dining area/ breakfast nook. Private en-suite with a walk-in closet for his and hers, QUARTZ dual sink vanity, and tiled shower.  The large family room perfect to gather with friends & family, has two expansive glass sliders, opens onto the 19x10 Florida room which leads to THE outdoor screened PATIO/DECK and provides a wonderful place for relaxation or entertainment all while overlooking fairways. The front patio IS ALSO covered WITH SCREENED lanai and so much more. This 24-hour manned, gated community offers outstanding recreational amenities, including an 18-hole championship golf course and restaurant, resort-style pool, fitness and spa center, tennis, pickleball, billiards and cards room, movie theater, art and craft facilities, library, community meeting room, walking and golf cart paths, among others. With lawn maintenance covered by the low HOA. This home, from the front curb to the backyard golf views, offers all that you are looking for! Furniture Negotiable!
